History of UI/UX
- **1980s**: GUI (Graphical User Interface) introduced by Apple.
- **1990s**: Rise of web design and usability.
- **2000s**: UX formalized as a discipline.
- **2010s–Present**: Mobile-first, responsive, and inclusive design dominate.
